"Okay, be careful, I'll wait for your update before making my next move, try to get closer to me."
"I've moved forward, still no ball in sight, I'll try to move left to get around the walls."
"I'll turn right to try to get a better angle, keep moving left and let me know if you see the ball."
"I've turned left and moved forward, still no ball, but I think I'm getting closer, I'll move left again."
